{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d09562a208","title":"在骂声中成长","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d03ae591cc","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":29,"articleId":"d09562a208"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4deb5ee98b","name":"清华大学八一一战斗小组"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d97189ab8d","type":"title","text":"在骂声中成长","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"1a4c4260af","type":"authors","text":"清华大学八一一战斗小组","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"7cab91f933","type":"paragraph","text":"在群众的泥巴里滚过千百万次的英雄才是真正的英雄。经过万千次考验的革命者才是真正的革命者。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"8e14b2bdc3","type":"paragraph","text":"谩骂和恐吓决不是战斗。但是字典中总还有那个\"骂\"字，因而骂声在生活中总是难免的。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"fead2e3a1c","type":"paragraph","text":"责骂和非难总是不可避免。真正的革命者是在骂声中成长的！","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"8e85db78f6","type":"paragraph","text":"骂声使混蛋发抖，骂声使政治庸人傍徨！","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"4225f04a2f","type":"paragraph","text":"骂声对革命者说来倒是一个小小的考验。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"e64f9724be","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的骂声，这是光荣，越发证明我们走的道路正确！","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"b117e9f6bf","type":"paragraph","text":"同志的\"骂声\"，这是误会，一旦真相大白，我们将更紧密团结！","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"4f75d7d795","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的骂声，使我们高兴，被敌人反对的是好事，而不是坏事！","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"4d0b240390","type":"paragraph","text":"同志的\"骂声\"，仗我们警戒，为革命坚持真理，修正错误！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"c44e7e0d1a","type":"paragraph","text":"对于敌人的骂声，我们嗤之以鼻，予以迎头痛击！","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"45599ed33e","type":"paragraph","text":"对于同志的\"骂声\"，我们认真听取，骂不当的给以热情的解释！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"8afc92e2a7","type":"paragraph","text":"沿着正确道路前进的人，送进耳中的敌人的骂声，将一浪高一浪。这是骄傲！坚定向前！","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"72d1032f92","type":"paragraph","text":"沿着错误道路前进的人，送进耳中的同志的\"骂声\"，将与日俱增。这是警告！回头是岸！","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"fef5a340a1","type":"paragraph","text":"劝同志之间的\"责骂\"可以休矣！","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"d842978ee6","type":"paragraph","text":"但愿敌人的叫骂声浪来得更猛烈些吧！","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"},{"id":"efc05f3582","type":"paragraph","text":"我们就是要在骂声中成长！","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208"}],"page":{"id":"8af9874bbb","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d09562a208","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}